    <page class="padded-page">
        <title size="2" class="matter-text small-title">Matter Replicator Failure</title>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">The Matter Replicator has a 5% fail chance.</text>
		<text class="matter-text text-block">If it happened you get Matter Dust with the exact same matter amount.</text>
		<text class="matter-text text-block">To get the matter out of it you have to put it into a Matter Recycler. From that you get Refined Matter Dust which can be decompost in the Matter Decomposer to get matter back.</text>
    </page>
